<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Takuya Asano</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f5f1ea;
        --text: #111111;
        --muted: #5f5a53;
        --line: #d8d1c8;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Hiragino Mincho ProN", "Yu Mincho", serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .wrap {
        width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 48px));
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      header {
        padding: 20px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .site-title {
        font-size: 14px;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 72px 0 56px;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
        align-items: end;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(42px, 8vw, 92px);
        line-height: 1;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .lead {
        margin-top: 18px;
        max-width: 34rem;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.9;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .panel {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding-top: 16px;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .section {
        padding: 28px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .section-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .works-list,
      .info-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .work-item {
        padding-bottom: 14px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .work-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
        padding-bottom: 0;
      }

      .work-title {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .work-meta,
      .info-text {
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      footer {
        padding: 40px 0 60px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 820px) {
        .hero {
          padding: 48px 0 40px;
        }

        .hero-grid,
        .section-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 20px;
        }

        .wrap {
          width: min(100% - 28px, 1100px);
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="site-title">Takuya Asano</div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="wrap hero-grid">
          <div>
            <h1>浅野託矢</h1>
            <p class="lead">
              ピアノを中心に、ポストクラシカル、アンビエント、
              エレクトロニカのあわいを行き来しながら制作と演奏を行っています。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            Musician / Composer<br />
            Sendai, Japan
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="wrap section-grid">
          <div class="section-title">Selected Works</div>
          <div class="works-list">
            <div class="work-item">
              <div class="work-title">Cinnamon</div>
              <div class="work-meta">Album</div>
            </div>
            <div class="work-item">
              <div class="work-title">Cucumber</div>
              <div class="work-meta">Album</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="wrap section-grid">
          <div class="section-title">Information</div>
          <div class="info-list">
            <div class="info-text">
              最新情報、音源、演奏に関する情報は今後ここに整理していきます。
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div class="wrap">© Takuya Asano</div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
